               <p>Do you know Bradbury? - Yes.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178309100023"></xptr>Do you recollect his being in the court before? - Yes, in 1782.</p>
               <p>Do you remember his being ordered to be transported for seven years? - Yes.</p>
               <p>GEORGE PEARCE sworn.</p>
               <p>I apprehended the prisoner at the bar.</p>
               <p>What was his behaviour at the time? - He behaved very well.</p>
               <p>He did not resist, but behaved very quietly? - Very easy, my Lord, he made no resistance at all.</p>
